e8a765e792175bbf6527808b5a8f97bc0530675a","tid":515120,"uid":148036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"坐巴士出去 榮(3:10PM上車)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/161307_56fa1c5cf7a956e67a0f69503109a9b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F161307_56fa1c5cf7a956e67a0f69503109a9b4.jpg&h=e49eb096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教教下色發覺草入面...南無阿彌陀佛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/161319_fba3cfb394bd94dafb36e7d7993b6208.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F161319_fba3cfb394bd94dafb36e7d7993b6208.JPG&h=447d0d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起坐地鐵舒服<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/161513_4edec33b83c026e04779e38143dde2c3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F161513_4edec33b83c026e04779e38143dde2c3.JPG&h=d17f55d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落車兒(大約4:15PM)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/161542_3379a4375cc8245e71c2ee94dcf517f4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F161542_3379a4375cc8245e71c2ee94dcf517f4.JPG&h=e8ef3380&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7408e53618079b697a5fb0c6c7a713cd6da80c6a","tid":515120,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"嘩長片， 拍得幾好 好有心機"},{"pid":"5bcb96a16db87b8b449c8aec39bd01944b0f3e1c","tid":515120,"uid":148036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7408e53618079b697a5fb0c6c7a713cd6da80c6a","tid":515120,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"嘩長片， 拍得幾好 好有心機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T08:29:11.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽到有人咁講真係好開心"},{"pid":"9f420a6c5449880bb6e3573b7d48a630d507b1b9","tid":515120,"uid":148036,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"住呢間the b nagoya hotel(榮)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/192506_6ed32555f83bb91f622da8b90679531c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F192506_6ed32555f83bb91f622da8b90679531c.jpg&h=11821f16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係到住1晚之後,<br />\n去金沢留一晚上立山黑部,再返黎住所以留個行李「喼」係到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/192524_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F192524_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg&h=dc4e8570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深夜1點都好啦通常D人好守秩序過馬路不論長短(見過6:00am可能趕返工除外XD)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/193008_96a02210c777e8cd3430141b384db716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F193008_96a02210c777e8cd3430141b384db716.jpg&h=68c8cd66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左名古屋駅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/193741_7c3a3115524dcadab8a7c8e46767aa75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F193741_7c3a3115524dcadab8a7c8e46767aa75.jpg&h=2e3b0688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買立山黑部用既車票$2XXX<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/194049_275b6487012d105f50494ce30d583381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F194049_275b6487012d105f50494ce30d583381.jpg&h=4dc52d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影貼紙相,夾下公仔＊有女團友係到,唔方便夾性感figure,講緊我FD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/194157_8bd99c62b6f946f638247686f549dc1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F194157_8bd99c62b6f946f638247686f549dc1b.jpg&h=68e9e077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個超難<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/194649_7ccd5cbc36c58e07097c7fc0ae63d411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F194649_7ccd5cbc36c58e07097c7fc0ae63d411.jpg&h=d2c113b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要等位，太餓然後我兩男丁分頭去第間排<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/194741_113c0b6a6a71a00acaef2f8a2a6b9788.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F194741_113c0b6a6a71a00acaef2f8a2a6b9788.JPG&h=6ff08aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間食串燒既,去到有位即入<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/195252_402a2dccb28d29238ec893488351576f.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F195252_402a2dccb28d29238ec893488351576f.PNG&h=4612c2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬上CALL佢地過黎,點知佢地係磯丸都入座了,叫我地過去<br />\n大佬我地水都飲左兩杯...係呢個女權既惡勢力下..<br />\n連忙鞠躬解釋抱歉抱歉...無錯我地賓返去磯丸...<br />\n(話說果日仲係同行個男丁生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"b40ef8f07d5722d7391290079aed1bf504276228","tid":515120,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:30:43.000Z","msg":"段片<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ce81172bc7c7ae571d0552fde3dd3a9c3e2a0a","tid":515120,"uid":64345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"段片出鏡最多男仔肯定日日同4條女啪啪啪，<br />\n戴眼鏡個男仔可能都有得玩既，但大部分時間就坐係隔離打飛機<br />\n最後肥肥地男仔同家僮、工人無咩分別，多數都係搬吓行李，睇地圖、食物焚化爐嗰類。<br />\n<br />\n至於4位女仕，咪又係韓妝雞"},{"pid":"a4dbffabeff8f4d868ff68d9